{"tid":302891,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"打細路咁撚小事都好吹嘘 真心低質","createTime":"2017-06-29T17:54:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-29T19:30:06.000Z","uid":71198,"like":4,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"32634fa30aef33ed9b23e2679cb6c00dd1cd4608","tid":302891,"uid":71198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T17:54:59.000Z","msg":"用手拉幾下 打幾下咋喎<br />\n有幾大件事呢請問？<br />\n又無用揸刀又無用其他武器<br />\n人地教自己細路關你撚事咩<br />\n大把人都俾老豆老母虐打過 <br />\n我都係其中一個 試過俾老豆打斷肋骨<br />\n<br />\n支持體罰請 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"825a66341d6eb21dc29d7773e312dda892d803f3","tid":302891,"uid":71198,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T18:01:37.000Z","msg":"個柒頭鄺俊乳即刻仆過去拎光環<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"672d8d0b5756fe49c8a2623f74a41c7de113aece","tid":302891,"uid":10894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T18:02:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"87f9081b9bc248abc91c51d3daf7d3cee1b38dc0","tid":302891,"uid":1134,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T18:03:25.000Z","msg":"打撚到你咁樣我好撚心痛"},{"pid":"14ed0c2d8c1c5dcfb0cafd2280e7ce39045f3836","tid":302891,"uid":57705,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T18:04:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a885b584aebda1f97ce65f5b17382c432eb36726","tid":302891,"uid":10894,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T18:05:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"aa65604274c24bca4f2b5b532ab9481024fd3535","tid":302891,"uid":71198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T18:07:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咪係, 想當年高登鬥慘大賽黎講, 條片真係小意思</blockquote><br />\n條片個老豆睇落都好輕手<br />\n當年我老豆係用高爾夫球棒鞭屍咁鞭<br />\n成床鼻血都繼續打 條片真心濕濕碎"},{"pid":"a26c9b638352025a596ecaec63da1020dd1bb61e","tid":302891,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T18:09:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b8446a817f93c0b569852